there are three types of awesome experience related with guru palace. dining in, parties, and catering. the restaurant is very beautiful inside and having good architecture inside. food is best. i tried so many times. if you eat there, you would feel like you are eating in a restaurant in India. a lot of varieties of appetizers and main course. party experience is also good. they have 2 big party halls and both are nice and pleasant. food is good. sitting and service is also awesome. you can have an awesome party there. you would listen from your guests that 'hmm, food is so good'. they also provide catering and its also good. i tried it once and i was fully satisfied with it. anyone should try it. it is a good restaurant.
